{"tid":610580,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無人權自修室都唔比訓覺","createTime":"2018-03-30T05:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T06:23:09.000Z","uid":179250,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"21fb3c29c23b24c0c29619fdb09da1af40c54cf0","tid":610580,"uid":179250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/133923_adc9fe3b2ea262b03ec3214375e49820.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F133923_adc9fe3b2ea262b03ec3214375e49820.png&h=32398d16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話說就考DSE既我<br />\n當然會去自修室溫下書啦<br />\n但係正常人係自修室溫書溫得奈<br />\n自然會眼訓架啦<br />\n唔通溫十幾個鐘都唔訓覺咩<br />\n就諗住係自修室張枱到訓5-10分鐘<br />\n訓唔夠5秒<br />\n就有職員大媽黎敲我張枱<br />\n話E到唔比訓覺🤦🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n仲要明明自修室仲有空位<br />\n做咩鳩姐你🤷🏿&zwj;♀️🤷🏿&zwj;♀️🤷🏿&zwj;♀️<br />\n成個自修室甘多廢老霸撚住d枱又唔見你做野<br />\n仲有覺得自修室唔比人訓覺勁唔人權lo"},{"pid":"1fbfacd2aa259651031bf641fcb9196507a938d0","tid":610580,"uid":36739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"21fb3c29c23b24c0c29619fdb09da1af40c54cf0","tid":610580,"uid":179250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/133923_adc9fe3b2ea262b03ec3214375e49820.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F133923_adc9fe3b2ea262b03ec3214375e49820.png&h=32398d16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話說就考DSE既我<br />\n當然會去自修室溫下書啦<br />\n但係正常人係自修室溫書溫得奈<br />\n自然會眼訓架啦<br />\n唔通溫十幾個鐘都唔訓覺咩<br />\n就諗住係自修室張枱到訓5-10分鐘<br />\n訓唔夠5秒<br />\n就有職員大媽黎敲我張枱<br />\n話E到唔比訓覺🤦🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n仲要明明自修室仲有空位<br />\n做咩鳩姐你🤷🏿&zwj;♀️🤷🏿&zwj;♀️🤷🏿&zwj;♀️<br />\n成個自修室甘多廢老霸撚住d枱又唔見你做野<br />\n仲有覺得自修室唔比人訓覺勁唔人權lo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:50:45.000Z","msg":"因為有人死過 <br />\n點知你死左定訓左"},{"pid":"c0bbc0db47252d8806de05d87c4d0fe76d0e2088","tid":610580,"uid":128164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim